  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified CLI for Harness services with resource-based commands",
    "Multi-format artifact registry management (Docker, npm, Maven, Python, Go, etc.)",
    "Flexible authentication with API keys, config files, and environment variables",
    "Registry migration from external sources (JFrog, Nexus)",
    "Remote Terraform plan execution with real-time log streaming",
    "JSON and table output formatting for all commands",
    "Artifact metadata management and firewall configuration"
